N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 562.9 - Enforcement of rules and regulations

State Regulations

The university police officers of the college have been
empowered to enforce traffic and parking rules and regulations. Tickets will be
issued to all vehicles which are not registered with the college and to
vehicles which are in violation of campus parking and/or traffic
regulations. Notes
